Package: opr
Title: OpenPrescribing in R
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Milan", "Wiedemann", email = "milan.wiedemann@gmail.com", comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-1991-282X"), role = c("aut", "cre")))
Description: Provides functions to connect to and query the OpenPrescribing.net
    BigQuery database. Helps researchers understand the available data and write
    readable, reusable, and modular queries for analysing English prescribing
    data using 'dplyr' and 'dbplyr' instead of SQL.
